HEADWORD: Jumpy
<hw>Jump"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <amorph>[<pos>Compar.</pos>
<adjf>Jumpier</adjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>superl.</pos>
<adjf>Jumpiest</adjf>.]</amorph> <def>Jumping, or inducing to jump;
characterized by jumps;</def> <specif>hence,</specif> <def>extremely
